Pink bikini wearing mudcrabs.  Anime eyes, hooker makeup and large boobs included.  Enjoy!

I didn\'t bother with a soundmod this time.  There\'s already some great ones out there though.

Install:

Copy the data folder in the archive to your Skyrim folder.
In the launcher, ensure that \'Load Loose Files\' is checked.
